hes, worms, a mysterious party, and an ancient curse that threatens the human race.<br><br>An adventure so delusional that it will make you delirious to the delirium itself!<br>Ha-Ha!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1272580/extras/9c271cf30b2b6d6249cb956756f52d71.poster.avif?t=1678321958\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1272580/extras/9c271cf30b2b6d6249cb956756f52d71.webm?t=1678321958\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1272580/extras/9c271cf30b2b6d6249cb956756f52d71.mp4?t=1678321958\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Truly and unique original story. (99.999999% GUARANTEED)</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Single player, dual character action-adventure with puzzle-solving elements.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Join professor Alexei Krakovitz and his loyal Japanese assistant, Akiro Kagasawa, in their heroic crusade against the Okkulte-55. </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Retro-pixel style artwork.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Meet a quirky cast of characters</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Visit Sundäe, a town oppressed by the Okkulte-55, on the northwest coast of Norway.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Talk with the dead</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1272580/extras/7b3d112fee522a56b29ca62921f029ba.poster.avif?t=1678321958\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1272580/extras/7b3d112fee522a56b29ca62921f029ba.webm?t=1678321958\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.a